    "title": "realtime lobby presence status with broadcast fallback",
    "description": "- Revert private:true on lobby channel (public channel sufficient for presence)\n- Add broadcast side-channel for realtime status propagation (in_match/available)\n- Apply status overrides on top of presence sync data\n- Refactor schema.sql into domain files (tables, functions, realtime)\n- Add DROP TRIGGER IF EXISTS guards for idempotent re-runs\n- Fix broadcast_match_update() to use realtime.send() with sanitized payload\n- Add INSERT+SELECT RLS policies for lobby channel",
