    "title": "add CSP headers, pre-commit hook, migrate inline styles, fix workflow permissions",
    "description": "- Add security headers (CSP, HSTS, X-Frame-Options) to vercel.json\n- Add pre-commit hook blocking .env file commits\n- Move inline styles from about-illustration.tsx to index.css\n- Restrict sync-commits workflow permissions and fix commit author\n- Remove hourly cron from sync-commits (push-only)\n- Add in-match presence status for RPS multiplayer\n- Delete .env.local with leaked VERCEL_OIDC_TOKEN\n- Create .env.example for developer onboarding",
